      "title": "On integrability properties of SU (2) Yang-Mills fields. I. Infinitesimal part",
      "abstract": "We study the distribution of 2\u2010plane elements on which infinitesimal parallel displacement of isovectors yields identity. This yields to an algebraic and differential classification and, in the generic case, to a quasimetric naturally associated with the field."
